author: Asif Lakhani
title: Yellow Jackets to square off against Seminoles in prime time
text:
Georgia Tech almost upset Florida State in the 2014 ACC Championship and now has the opportunity to do it again, this time at home.
According to a release, the Yellow Jackets' homecoming game against Seminoles on Saturday, Oct. 24, will kick off at 7 p.m. and be televised on ESPN 2.
The Seminoles are 6-0 on the season and undefeated in ACC play (4-0).
PHOTOS: Georgia Tech loses to Pittsburgh The Yellow Jackets lost a close game to Pittsburgh at home Saturday.
